   "source": [
    "# Eclares - Clarity-driven Ergodic Search\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook runs the full Eclares simulation for autonomous oceanographic coverage with quadrotor systems. All modules are imported from the `Eclares` package."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import Pkg; Pkg.activate(joinpath(@__DIR__, "..")); Pkg.instantiate()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "using Eclares\n",
    "using LinearAlgebra\n",
    "using Plots"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Run Simulation\n",
    "\n",
    "Simulate the quadrotor coverage mission with battery replacement. Flight modes:\n",
    "- **Mission**: Following nominal coverage trajectories\n",
    "- **Landing**: Return to charging station when battery is low"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Initial state: [position(3), quaternion(4), velocity(3), angular_velocity(3), state_of_charge]\n",
    "uhover = Eclares.QuadSys.uhover\n",
    "r0 = [0.0; 0.0; 0.0]\n",
    "q0 = Eclares.QuaternionUtils.L([1.0; 0.0; 0; 0]) * Eclares.QuaternionUtils.rptoq([0.; 0; 0])\n",
    "v0 = zeros(3)\n",
    "ω0 = zeros(3)\n",
    "init_SOC = 40.\n",
    "x0 = [r0; q0; v0; ω0; init_SOC]\n",
    "\n",
    "T_SIM = 60.0  # Simulation time in seconds"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "sol = Eclares.EclaresSim.simulate(x0, 0., T_SIM)\n",
    "X1 = sol.u\n",
    "T = sol.t\n",
    "println(\"Simulation complete. States: \$(length(sol.u)), Time steps: \$(length(sol.t))\")"
   ]
  },
